𝟮𝟱 𝗠𝗜𝗡 𝗖𝗜𝗥𝗖𝗨𝗜𝗧 - ladder up, and down!⁣

• 5 burpee⁣
• 10 jump lunges ⁣
• 20 heismans⁣
• 30 line chips ⁣
• 40 mountain climbers⁣
• 50 toe to jump⁣
• 60 bicycles⁣
